Lead the effective development, customization and periodic upgrade of P&WC’s CRM system while maintaining in-depth knowledge of the state-of-the art across various industries and ensuring P&WC benefits from that knowledge. This includes prioritizing upgrades, developing specifications as well as developing test scenarios and the means to have them executed.
Drive the effective and sophisticated use of P&WC data and the integration of external data sources to ensure the fullest picture of our customers and competitive landscape is obtained in the most efficient fashion.
Play a lead role in driving improved customer experience by developing means to drive customer-centric key performance indicators, access to data, and more effective customer management tools.
